ChangeLog for paludis-utils
===========================

This file lists every change made except typo and formatting fixes.

2008-06-26 Ali Polatel

	* putils/lscolours.py: Cache LS_COLORS output to make colourizing
	faster.

	* +putils/lscolours.py, putils/__init__.py, putils/applets/plist.py:
	Add coloured output for plist using LS_COLORS environment variable.

2008-06-24 Ali Polatel

	* putils/applets/plist.py, putils/applets/psize.py, putils/getopt.py:
	Merge query and advanced query options

	* scripts/p: Nicer help display

	* putils/applets/pfile.py, putils/packages.py: Add content limiting
	options to pfile

	* putils/packages.py: Make content check earlier.

	* putils/packages.py: Smarter ROOT handling
	
	* +putils/applets/pfile.py, putils/applets/__init__.py,
	putils/packages.py: Added new applet pfile

	* putils/applets/plist.py, putils/applets/psize.py,
	putils/packages.py: Use generators

	* putils/applets/plist.py, putils/applets/psize.py, putils/getopt.py:
	Remove redundant quoting

2008-06-18 Ali Polatel

	* putils/applets/patom.py, putils/applets/plist.py,
	putils/applets/psize.py, scripts/p: Moved signal handling to virtual
	applet.

2008-06-17 Ali Polatel

	* putils/getopt.py, putils/packages.py: Fixed -S/--selection.

	* putils/applets/plist.py, putils/applets/psize.py, putils/getopt.py,
	putils/packages.py: Better content limiting.

2008-06-16 Ali Polatel

	* scripts/p: Check for error when importing applets.

	* putils/applets/patom.py, putils/getopt.py, putils/packages.py:
	Updated for paludis head. Change parse_user_package_dep_spec usage.
	Use GIT_HEAD instead of SUBVERSION_REVISION. Add -E option to patom
	now that it's required by parse_user_package_dep_spec.

2008-06-08 Ali Polatel

	* putils/getopt.py, putils/packages.py: Make -S/--selection smarter

2008-06-05 Ali Polatel

	* +putils/common.py, putils/__init__.py, putils/applets/plist.py,
	putils/applets/psize.py: Add signal handlers

	* putils/applets/plist.py, putils/applets/psize.py, putils/getopt.py,
	putils/packages.py: Remove -w option, make it default

	* putils/applets/plist.py, putils/applets/psize.py,
	putils/packages.py: Added -R option to match by source repository.

2008-06-04 Ali Polatel

	* putils/applets/plist.py, putils/applets/psize.py,
	putils/packages.py: Fix ROOT handling. Add -r option to plist.

	* putils/applets/patom.py, putils/applets/plist.py,
	putils/applets/psize.py: Use <pkgname>...  in usage to make it clear
	that the applets can receive more than one package name as argument.

	* putils/applets/patom.py, putils/applets/plist.py,
	putils/applets/psize.py, scripts/p: s/_applet_usage/usage

	* putils/applets/__init__.py, putils/packages.py,
	+putils/applets/patom.py: Added new applet patom

	* setup.py: Added classifiers

	* (lots): Initial version
